# tiny-elastic-cli #

A simple cli for querying elasticsearch. Outputs json.

## Config ## 

Launching the cli once will propagate ~/.tiny-elastic-cli.conf

## Usage ##

`elastic --help`

`elastic 'foo:bar' 

`elastic 'foo:bar' --source 'otherfield' | jq .`

### Installing ###

`pip install tiny-elastic-cli`

